#Movie Name: Vijay talwal
## story

### He has the creticivity he always do something exrtra. He found his girlfriends after accident. He got an idea when happen if i will make a device that has a sim after accident it will send notification to my friends, police, ambullance, and nearby hospital. No one trusting on his app. he belongs to very poor family. His girlfriend is also not trusting on him. After his girlfriend he also stop drinking, which he can't able to discontinue. after his all try his girlfriend also leave him alone. Sometimes he has doubt on himself. on day his father remember his one line "you know in our generation untill something not happen we didnot stop that but in your generation if something is not happen you stop working on that and donot trying to find how it will happen. He start again with full energy. He try to meet people who has a little trust on his app. later he go to mumbai, he make a demo of project, but due to one managemnt employee he got assamed. He breakup from core. finally without any permision he do the demo. finally app was launch. 
